        "class": "",
        "text": "With respect to the Nethinim, whom David and the princes (of Israel) had given for the service of the Levites (i.e., made servants of the temple, to perform the lowest offices for the Levites), comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Joshua 9:21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 2:43",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". \"They all were distinguished by name,\" i.e., were men of note; comp. remarks on ",
        "children": []
      },
